<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Voided Studios</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #0f0f14;
      color: white;
    }

    header {
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #1a1a24;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    header p {
      color: #aaa;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    section {
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .card {
      background: #1a1a24;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #777;
      background: #1a1a24;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    a {
      color: #7aa2ff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>Voided Studios</h1>
  <p>Built by AgentXCO2 for creative intelligence and next generation interaction</p>
</header>

<section>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>Voided Studios is a developer studio creating AI systems, tools, and experimental software projects.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <p>VoidGPT - AI assistant system</p>
    <p>Void APIs - backend tools and services</p>
    <p>Void Defender - security system tools</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Licensing</h2>
    <p>All Voided Studios projects are licensed under Mozilla Public License Version 2.0 unless stated otherwise.</p>
    <p>View license details: <a href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/MPL/2.0/">MPL 2.0</a></p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Studio Owner: AgentXCO2</p>
  </div>

</section>

<footer>
  © 2026 Voided Studios
</footer>

</body>
</html>
